============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- DESKTOP_API_DISABLED
- DESKTOP_LOCAL_BRIDGE_DISABLED
- DESKTOP_LOCAL_BRIDGE_BLOCKED
- DESKTOP_UPDATE_NOT_CONFIGURED
- LAUNCH_DISABLED
- WAITLIST_DISABLED
- INVITE_CODE_INVALID
- INVITE_CODE_EXPIRED
- INVITE_CODE_REVOKED
- LAUNCH_READINESS_BLOCKED
- PUBLIC_STATUS_DISABLED
- TELEMETRY_DISABLED
- DISTRIBUTION_DISABLED
- PACKAGE_NOT_FOUND
- PACKAGE_SIGNING_NOT_CONFIGURED
- PACKAGE_SECURITY_REVIEW_REQUIRED
- MARKETPLACE_PUBLISH_BLOCKED
- DESKTOP_RELEASE_NOT_FOUND
- ENTERPRISE_BUNDLE_SECRET_CONFIRMATION_REQUIRED
- INSTALLER_MANIFEST_INVALID
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

